<item>
            <title>[SOLR-3820] Solr Admin Query form is missing some edismax request parameters</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3820</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following edismax parameters are missing from the Solr Admin Query form:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;uf - User Fields&lt;br/&gt;
pf2 - bigram phrase boost fields&lt;br/&gt;
pf3 - trigram phrase boost fields&lt;br/&gt;
ps2 - phrase slop for bigram phrases&lt;br/&gt;
ps3 - phrase slop for trigram phrases&lt;br/&gt;
boost - multiplicative boost function&lt;br/&gt;
stopwords - remove stopwords from mandatory &quot;matching&quot; component (true/false, defaults to true)&lt;br/&gt;
lowercaseOperators - Enable lower-case &quot;and&quot; and &quot;or&quot; as operators (true/false, defaults to true)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The ability to set field name aliases is also missing: f.myalias.qf=realfield.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
